snippet.title: THE PATHLESS | Coming to Switch and Xbox February 2
snippet.description:
The Pathless is coming to Nintendo Switch and Xbox on February 2nd: https://thepathless.com

From the creators of ABZÛ, The Pathless is the mythic adventure of an archer and an eagle in a vast forest. Become the Hunter, a master of archery who travels to a mystical island to dispel a curse of darkness that grips the world.

Developed by GIANT SQUID. Published by Annapurna Interactive.

© Annapurna Interactive, 2023
